title: Speech perception experiment. Earn $1.50 for 15 minutes.
description: Listen to audio clips and type what you hear. Please only participate if you are a native speaker of English, and at most speak a few words of another language.
Answer.comments: This survey said it would take 15 minutes, there is absolutely no way it could be done that quickly.  I am at the 30 min mark now and I know that others could do it quicker but no way 15 minutes.  It is not fair for requesters to do this to workers because now I have made what amounts to $3/hr.  I (nor most others) would accept a HIT that takes 30min for only $1.50.  I hope you will consider shortening this or paying more in the future.
